diff --git a/CHANGES.rst b/CHANGES.rst
index 2db769f..91ee3e7 100644
--- a/CHANGES.rst
+++ b/CHANGES.rst
@@ -62,6 +62,10 @@ Unreleased
 -   Contexts created during shell completion are closed properly, fixing
     ``ResourceWarning``s when using ``click.File``. :issue:`2644` :pr:`2800`
     :pr:`2767`
+-   ``click.edit()`` supports editing multiple files at once by passing an
+    iterable of filenames to ``filename``.
+-   ``click.edit()`` gained a ``process_priority`` parameter to control the
+    CPU priority of the launched editor process.
 
 
 Version 8.1.8
